name: ircSEX Messenger
tagline: An amazing irc client for Android
body:
### ircSEX Messenger
ircSEX Messenger is a new take on irc clients for the Android platform. Our vision is that irc doesn't have to look like a terminal or hacker chat, we take inspiration from modern messaging platforms such as Google Hangouts when designing this irc client.


### Authors and Contributors
This project is driven by 
* Alexander "Hult↓" Hultnér @hultner
* Joel "oed" Thorstensson @oed
* Wilhelm "Heiß" Hedman @hedmanw
* Johan "Jühan" Magnusson @jcmmagnusson
* Oskar "Rascal" Nyberg @raksooo
